<b>
<a href="http://www.ralloszek.net/ubbthreads/showthreaded.php?Cat=&amp;Board=rp&amp;Number=14024&amp;page=0&amp;view=collapsed&amp;sb=5&amp;o=&amp;vc=1" target="_new" title="Re: to post #14024" alt="Re: to post #14024">Broken from the wars...</a>
</b>
 <img alt="new" src="/ubbthreads/images/new.gif" />
 
